name: 布鲁诺·杜博
birth_place: 美国,得克萨斯州,布莱恩
introduction: Bruno Dubeux was born in Bryan, Texas to Brazilian parents. He is a member of the traditional Burle Dubeux family, a Pernambucan family of French descent. When he was born, his parents were university students and they were in the United States. He left his hometown of Bryan, Texas, only 3 months old when his parents returned to Recife, Pernambuco.He holds a degree in Medicine from the Federal University of Pernambuco with a postgraduate degree in pediatrics at the University of Porto and a year of internship at the Harvard Medical School and a degree in Performing Arts from UniverCidade.
